  "page": "Garth IX Gardener",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For others with the same name, see <a href=\"/index.php/Garth_Gardener\" title=\"Garth Gardener\">Garth Gardener</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Garth\" title=\"Garth\">Garth</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\"><img alt=\"House Gardener.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/50px-House_Gardener.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/75px-House_Gardener.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/100px-House_Gardener.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Garth IX Gardener</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\"><img alt=\"House Gardener.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/50px-House_Gardener.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/75px-House_Gardener.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/100px-House_Gardener.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Reign</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Coming_of_the_Andals\" title=\"Coming of the Andals\">Coming of the Andals</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nGarth of House Gardener, the Ninth of His Name</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Reach\" title=\"King of the Reach\">King of the Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Heir</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Merle_I_Gardener\" title=\"Merle I Gardener\">Merle I Gardener</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Successor</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Merle_I_Gardener\" title=\"Merle I Gardener\">Merle I Gardener</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\">House Gardener</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Merle_I_Gardener\" title=\"Merle I Gardener\">Merle I Gardener</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Garth IX Gardener</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Reach\" title=\"King of the Reach\">King of the Reach</a> and head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\">House Gardener</a>. Along with his son <a href=\"/index.php/Merle_I_Gardener\" title=\"Merle I Gardener\">Merle I</a> and grandson <a href=\"/index.php/Gwayne_V_Gardener\" title=\"Gwayne V Gardener\">Gwayne V</a>, he is remembered as one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sage_Kings\" title=\"Three Sage Kings\">Three Sage Kings</a> who dealt with the <a href=\"/index.php/Coming_of_the_Andals\" title=\"Coming of the Andals\">coming of the Andals</a> to the Reach with a policy of accord and assimilation rather then armed resistance.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf773_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf773-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Garth_IX_Gardener&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Garth was wise and cunning.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf773_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf773-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Garth_IX_Gardener&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Instead of fighting off the <a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a>, Garth IX brought a <a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">septon</a> to his court and made him part of his councils. The first <a href=\"/index.php/Sept\" title=\"Sept\">sept</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a> was built during Garth's reign, although he continued to worship the <a href=\"/index.php/Old_gods\" title=\"Old gods\">old gods</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Godswood_of_Highgarden\" title=\"Godswood of Highgarden\">godswood of Highgarden</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf773_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf773-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Garth took Andals into his service as household <a href=\"/index.php/Knights\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Knights\">knights</a> and retainers, and he bequeathed lands and wives and lordships for the more powerful of the Andal kings and other Andal adventurers descending on the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a> in exchange for pledges of fealty.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf773_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf773-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Garth also sought after Andal craftsmen, especially blacksmiths and stonemasons, to settle throughout the Reach, supplying him and his bannermen with <a href=\"/index.php/Iron\" title=\"Iron\">iron</a> instead of <a href=\"/index.php/Bronze\" title=\"Bronze\">bronze</a> and strengthening their castles and holdfasts with Andal masonry.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf773_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf773-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Garth_IX_Gardener&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>When a <a href=\"/index.php/Wolf\" title=\"Wolf\">wolf</a> descends upon your flocks, all you gain by killing him is a short respite, for other wolves will come. If instead you feed the wolf and tame him and turn his pups into your guard <a href=\"/index.php/Dog\" title=\"Dog\">dogs</a>, they will protect the flock when the pack comes ravening.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf773_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf773-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Garth IX Gardener</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Garth_IX_Gardener&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Garth IX</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a><br />wife</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" col